'''Synergia Ranch''' is an [[ecovillage]] founded in 1969 by [[John P. Allen]], the inventor and former Director of Research of [[Biosphere 2]] and Marie Harding, its present manager.
Synergia Ranch operates as a private retreat and workshop center for small groups. It is located in [[Santa Fe County, New Mexico]], 15 miles south of the city of [[Santa Fe, New Mexico|Santa Fe]].
